alse},"blocks":{}},"text_YHXXxE":{"type":"text","name":"t:blocks.text.name","settings":{"text":"<p>Si tu produis mais que tout sonne “déjà entendu”, ce programme est <strong>ton point de rupture.</strong> L’Alchimiste t’apprend à créer et assembler les sons, et en faire en signature personnelle. Synthèse, sampling, modulation, traitement, <strong>le sound design n'aura plus aucun secret pour toi</strong>. Tu apprendras à <strong>créer, transformer et maîtriser le son en profondeur</strong>, jusqu’à forger une identité sonore qui te distingue immédiatement.<br/><br/></p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"text-base","text_max_size":32,"text_line_height":1.6,"text_letter_spacing":0,"text_capitalize":false,"secondary_color":false,"width":"fit-content","custom_width":100,"alignment":"left","width_mobile":"fit-content","custom_width_mobile":100,"effects":"none","highlighted_text":"text","highlighted_scribble":"circle"},"blocks":{}},"video_qFrLEy":{"type":"video","name":"t:blocks.video.name","settings":{"source":"uploaded","video":"shopify://files/videos/Wesbite - Présentation - L'alchimiste.mp4","video_url":"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=_9VUPq3SxOc","description":"","aspect_ratio":"adapt","enable_video_autoplay":false,"enable_video_looping":true,"source_mobile":"uploaded","video_mobile":"shopify://files/videos/Wesbite - Présentation - L'alchimiste.mp4","video_url_mobile":"","description_mobile":"","aspect_ratio_mobile":"adapt","width":"fill","custom_width":100,"width_mobile":"fill","custom_width_mobile":100,"border":"none","border_width":1,"border_opacity":100,"border_radius":24},"blocks":{}},"spacer_8amLGJ":{"type":"spacer","name":"t:blocks.spacer.name","settings":{"size":"percent","percent_size":100,"pixel_size":120,"custom_mobile_size":false,"size_mobile":"percent","percent_size_mobile":100,"pixel_size_mobile":120},"blocks":{}},"custom_liquid_pLCaqA":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.name","settings":{"liquid":"<h2 style=\"\n  font-size: 18px;\n  font-weight: bold;\n\">\n  CE QUE TU VAS APPRENDRE : \n</h2>"},"blocks":{}},"spacer_Mrxp8q":{"type":"spacer","name":"t:blocks.spacer.name","disabled":true,"settings":{"size":"percent","percent_size":100,"pixel_size":120,"custom_mobile_size":false,"size_mobile":"percent","percent_size_mobile":100,"pixel_size_mobile":120},"blocks":{}},"text_FDwKdW":{"type":"text","name":"t:blocks.text.name","settings":{"text":"<p>• <strong>Créer des sons uniques à partir de zéro</strong> et ne plus dépendre des presets<br/>• <strong>Comprendre la synthèse wavetable en profondeur</strong> pour maîtriser la matière sonore<br/>• <strong>Maîtriser les modulations, matrices et routings avancés</strong> avec précision<br/>• <strong>Transformer un preset banal en signature sonore</strong> personnelle<br/>• <strong>Construire des textures complexes mais maîtrisées</strong> et cohérentes<br/>• <strong>Adapter un son à son contexte musical</strong> avec justesse<br/>• Produire des sons qui <strong>simplifient le mix au lieu de le compliquer</strong><br/>• <strong>Développer une identité sonore reconnaissable dès les premières secondes</strong><br/>• Passer d’utilisateur de plugin à <strong>véritable designer sonore</strong><br/>• <strong>Forger une palette sonore qui t’appartient</strong> et qui te distingue</p>","text_font":"body","text_size":"text-base","text_max_size":32,"text_line_height":1.6,"text_letter_spacing":0,"text_capitalize":false,"secondary_color":false,"width":"fit-content","custom_width":100,"alignment":"left","width_mobile":"fit-content","custom_width_mobile":100,"effects":"none","highlighted_text":"text","highlighted_scribble":"circle"},"blocks":{}},"spacer_FYBerF":{"type":"spacer","name":"t:blocks.spacer.name","settings":{"size":"percent","percent_size":100,"pixel_size":120,"custom_mobile_size":false,"size_mobile":"percent","percent_size_mobile":100,"pixel_size_mobile":120},"blocks":{}},"custom_liquid_fdxk9q":{"type":"custom-liquid","name":"t:sections.custom-liquid.name","